        "title": "fix: show official owner badges across public surfaces",
        "body": "## Summary\n- Compute `owner.official` for public skill detail responses and the main `/skills` list response from the existing hard-coded OpenClaw publisher policy.\n- Preserve `owner.official` through `/api/v1/packages/:name` so plugin detail pages can render the compact owner badge.\n- Render compact Official badges when either the skill badge is official or the owner is official.\n- Clean local moderation fixtures so `local-agentic-risk-demo` is not official from stale seeded badges or stale `local` membership in the `openclaw` publisher.\n\n## Validation\n- `bun run test convex/skills.public.test.ts convex/skills.publicListCursor.test.ts convex/httpApiV1.handlers.test.ts packages/schema/src/schemas.test.ts src/components/SkillListItem.test.tsx src/__tests__/package-detail-route.test.tsx`\n- `bun run format:check`\n- `bun run lint`\n- `VITE_CONVEX_URL=https://example.invalid bunx tsc --noEmit`\n- `bunx tsc -p packages/schema/tsconfig.json --noEmit`\n- `bunx tsc -p packages/clawhub/tsconfig.json --noEmit`\n- `bunx convex dev --once`\n- `bunx convex run devSeed:seedLocalFixtures '{\"reset\":false}'`\n\n## Local UI Check\nChecked locally at `http://127.0.0.1:3000` after reseeding dev Convex:\n\n| Route | Result |\n| --- | --- |\n| `/skills?sort=downloads` | `Steipete Shortcuts` has 1 Official badge; `Codex Owner Move Debug` has 1 Official badge from `owner.official`; `Local Agentic Risk Demo` has 0 Official badges. |\n| `/steipete/codex-owner-move-debug-1778257045` | skill detail has Official title tag and compact owner Official badge. |\n| `/plugins/@openclaw/whatsapp` | plugin detail has Official title tag and compact owner Official badge. |\n| `skills:getBySlug {\"slug\":\"local-agentic-risk-demo\"}` | `owner` has no `official` field and `skill.badges` is `{}`. |\n",
